Usage:
  rails generate zen:api ModelName [field:type field:type]

Description:
    Generates an API CRUD controller with rswag tests.

    This generates:
        - API controller with CRUD actions (index, show, create, update, destroy)
        - rswag test specs for Swagger documentation
        - Routes for the resource

Example:
    rails generate zen:api Article title:string body:text status:integer

    This will create:
        - app/controllers/api/v1/articles_controller.rb
        - spec/requests/api/v1/articles_spec.rb
        - Adds routes to config/routes.rb

    To generate Swagger documentation:
        bundle exec rspec spec/requests/api/v1/articles_spec.rb --format Rswag::Specs::SwaggerFormatter
